      "content": "That's not helpful. You're the logistics coordinator assigned to our account, so you should have the manifest and the transit logs right in front of you. If you tell me you \"don't have access,\" my manager is going to think you're just dodging responsibility for the delay so you don't have to pay out the penalty. \n\nJust tell me the truth: is it stuck in customs? Or is it actually on a truck nearby? I just need a straight answer so I can decide whether to start the claims process.",
